    "lines": [
      {"speaker": "莉莉", "chinese": "下星期我就要回国了,我来向您告别。", "pinyin": "Xià xīngqī wǒ jiù yào huí guó le, wo lái xiàng nín gào bié.", "english": "I'm going back to my country next week. I've come to say goodbye to you."},
      {"speaker": "老师", "chinese": "行李都收拾好了吗?", "pinyin": "Xíngli dõu shōushi hảo le ma?", "english": "Have you packed all your luggage?"},
      {"speaker": "莉莉", "chinese": "都收拾好了。", "pinyin": "Dõu shōushi hảo le.", "english": "Yes, all packed."},
      {"speaker": "小叶", "chinese": "莉莉,今天我们给你饯行,祝你一路平安。", "pinyin": "Lìli, jīntiān wǒmen gěi nǐ jiànxíng, zhù nǐ yī lù píng'ān.", "english": "Lili, today we're giving you a farewell dinner. Wishing you a safe journey."},
      {"speaker": "莉莉", "chinese": "我也祝你们生活幸福,工作顺利。", "pinyin": "Wǒ yě zhù nǐmen shēnghuó xìngfú, gōngzuò shùnlì.", "english": "I also wish you all a happy life and smooth work."},
      {"speaker": "���叶", "chinese": "刚来中国的时候,你连一句汉语也不会说。现在说得真不错。", "pinyin": "Gāng lái Zhōngguó de shíhou, nĩ lián yì jù Hànyŭ yě bu huì shuo. Xiànzài shuō de zhẽn búcuò.", "english": "When you first came to China, you couldn't speak even one sentence of Chinese. Now you speak really well."},
      {"speaker": "莉莉", "chinese": "你们给了我很多��助,我真不知道怎么感谢你们才好。", "pinyin": "Nimen gěile wo hěn duō bãngzhù. wo zhen bu zhīdào zěnme gănxiè nimen cái hão.", "english": "You've given me so much help. I don't know how to thank you enough."},
      {"speaker": "小叶", "chinese": "我们真舍不得你走。", "pinyin": "Wǒmen zhēn shěbude nǐ zǒu.", "english": "We really hate to see you go."},
      {"speaker": "小叶", "chinese": "来,大家举杯,为我们的友谊干杯。", "pinyin": "Lái, dàjiā jǔ bēi, wèi wǒmen de yǒuyì gān bēi.", "english": "Come on, everyone. Let's raise our glasses to our friendship!"}
